text:
hey <@UDNSVHW2K>, `INVALID_ASSOCIATION_PROPERTY ` normally points to an error with the association property not corresponding to an existing object. See the `association properties` section here: <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/methods/ecomm-bridge/ecomm-bridge-overview>

If you’re still lost I’m happy to take a look if you send over the request URL including the method, the raw request body (including the headers), and the full error response you receive from HubSpot.

Omit any sensitive details!
